org.sxb.session.web.http

インタフェース RequestResponsePostProcessor

  • 既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    MultiHttpSessionStrategy
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:

    public interface RequestResponsePostProcessor
    Allows customizing the HttpServletRequest and/or the HttpServletResponse.
    導入されたバージョン:
    1.0
    作成者:
    Jeffson

    • メソッドの概要

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest wrapRequest(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response)
      Allows customizing the HttpServletRequest.
      javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse wrapResponse(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response)
      Allows customizing the HttpServletResponse.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • wrapRequest

        javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest wrapRequest(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                                                  javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response)
        Allows customizing the HttpServletRequest.
        パラメータ:
        request - the original HttpServletRequest. Cannot be null.
        response - the original HttpServletResponse. This is NOT the result of wrapResponse(HttpServletRequest, HttpServletResponse) Cannot be null. .
        戻り値:
        a non-null HttpServletRequest

      • wrapResponse

        javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse wrapResponse(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                                                    javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response)
        Allows customizing the HttpServletResponse.
        パラメータ:
        request - the original HttpServletRequest. This is NOT the result of wrapRequest(HttpServletRequest, HttpServletResponse). Cannot be null.
        response - the original HttpServletResponse. Cannot be null.
        戻り値:
        a non-null HttpServletResponse
